1. Changelog
============
This is a non-exhaustive (but still near complete) changelog for Tweet Display Back,
including beta and release candidate versions.
Our thanks to all those people who've contributed bug reports and code fixes.

Legend:

* - Security Fix
# - Bug Fix
$ - Language fix or change
+ - Addition
^ - Change
- - Removed
! - Note

14-June-2013 Michael Babker
! [#64] Raise minimum supported version to 2.5.6 due to lack of autoload support
^ [#59] Manually filter retweets due to apparent API discontinuation

13-June-2013 Jurian Even
^ [#63] Add scheme to helper.php to support https://

10-June-2013 Michael Babker
# [#60] Two Twitter feed modules with cache on - both modules erroneously display the same content

